			z(o) -----------> 0.0002587532
			[fe/h] ---------> -2.058141258363775
			[sr/h] ---------> -1.8831288138453521
			[o/h] ----------> -1.3445102993763647
			[sr/fe] --------> 0.17501244451842268
			[o/fe] ---------> 0.7136309589874101
			[o/sr] ---------> 0.5386185144689875
